reviewText: Very well done; would recommend it to anyone interested in life on earth.
Who knew??  Well, chemists and geologists and biologists probably had an idea, but this is a wonderful and entertaining take for the rest of us.
Saw this on PBS and wanted to get my own copy to watch. Very good explanation of the earth formation. Talks about the properties of rocks and crystals.
Watched this over and over again
NOVA always does a great job.
The DVD would not play in three different machines so I never watched it and had to return it. Disappointing!
Very good video about Planet history.
